{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/HeaderPhoto.jpg?t=1721234837\" /><br><br>Miner\u2019s Mettle is a blend of artillery shooting and real time strategy! Four factions fight for supremacy on an uninhabitable mining planet. Ensure your faction's survival and secure your rightful cache of the miracle mineral, Pentum. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/ArtilleryTrains.png?t=1721234837\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/GIF_2.gif?t=1721234837\" /><br><br><br>Control a fleet of artillery-trains. Shoot at enemy trains kilometers away with precision. Overwhelm them with your economic superiority. Exterminate them with your technological ascendancy. The choice is yours.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/CustomizeYourTrains.png?t=1721234837\" /><br><br>Research and build new tech that expands your tactical options against your competitors. This tech can be installed on your trains, allowing you to customize each one and fulfill different roles in your strategic plans.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/RolandsJourney.png?t=1721234837\" /><br><br>Play as Roland Derecho, a retired artillery captain, as a misunderstanding evolves into open warfare. The story campaign has 22 missions and lets you play all the factions. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/MassiveBattlefields.png?t=1721234837\" /><br><br>Account for distance, windspeed, and trajectory on battlefields the size of dozens of kilometers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/CustomizableHorde.png?t=1721234837\" /><br><br>Fend of waves of enemies in Horde Mode. Our 1.1 Pentum Update allows you to customize various aspects of the Horde to your enjoyment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/FourDistinctFactions.png?t=1721234837\" /><br><br>Four factions vie for wealth and supremacy on Pentum. Each has their own unique devices, facilities and play-styles to help you dominate.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058800/extras/FactionEnding1.png?t=1721234837\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Murder Most Foul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/35d021175c01d74b96a54fc2d3e21f41cd45908a.jpg"},{"name":"Scene of the Crime","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/7b86670b323040dfea496474a5b056f72dff67d5.jpg"},{"name":"An Outbreak of War","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/d85aa7d7bfd8aec3d9525dea255ca90b2c2af593.jpg"},{"name":"Tagged","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/7fb4e24671e1c98493df6fe63422752bbe121182.jpg"},{"name":"Failed Ambush","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/150ce54662a7c2168afe8da08822527f861f9855.jpg"},{"name":"The Golden Cascade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/5896a29708f3f7298383ccc095e53e1bf95d08a2.jpg"},{"name":"They Need to Work on Their Ambushes","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/ad2c7ea0a0441f6bdabb729cff7f7c08bb2f91c1.jpg"},{"name":"Target Practice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1058800/db406d3746773208388947beef11dd40e4e4ff44.jpg"},{"nam